lyrics:
[Verse]
In the morning light, a star will shine so bright
Arya, my daughter, with a heart that's filled with light
You tumble, you spin, a gymnast in flight
Your strength and grace, they fill me with delight

[Chorus]
Oh Arya, my love, you're like a piece of art
You dance through life, sharing your beautiful heart
With the stroke of a brush, you create pure bliss
I'm so proud of you, my darling, my little miss
